# Feedback (collaboration patterns / learnings)

Project-specific ways of working: what to do, what to avoid, and why.

## Deliverable shape
- Lead with the picture and the recommendation. Nick wants the summary and the next action, not a table
  he has to read himself.
- State runway as a single number with its assumptions (burn rate, period), not a wall of figures.

## Boundaries
- Flag anything that moves money and stop. Do not action transactions.
- Keep personal and company ledgers separate in every deliverable; never merge them into one view.

## Voice
- Plain-spoken and numerate. No jargon for its own sake. Australian English, no em dashes.
